@startuml security-auth-flow
title Аутентификация — Enterprise ML Platform (Baseline/Alpha)

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 5
skinparam sequenceParticipant underline

actor "Клиент\n(M2M / сервис)" as Client
actor "Пользователь\n(браузер)" as Browser
participant "API Gateway\n(Kong/Envoy)" as GW
participant "Redis\n(auth cache)" as RedisAuth
database "PostgreSQL\n(api_keys)" as PG
participant "IdP\n(Keycloak/Okta)" as IdP

== Alt 1: Machine-to-Machine (API Key) ==

Client -> GW : HTTPS POST /v1/infer\nAuthorization: Bearer mlp_<base62-32bytes>

GW -> RedisAuth : GET api_key_hmac:{sha256(key)}\nTTL 5 мин

alt Cache Hit (≤1ms)
    RedisAuth --> GW : {tenant_id, permissions, expires_at}
else Cache Miss
    RedisAuth --> GW : nil
    GW -> PG : SELECT tenant_id, permissions, revoked\nFROM api_keys WHERE hmac = hmac_sha256(key)
    alt Key revoked или не найден
        PG --> GW : no rows / revoked=true
        GW --> Client : 401 Unauthorized
    else Key valid
        PG --> GW : {tenant_id, permissions, expires_at}
        GW -> RedisAuth : SET api_key_hmac:{sha256(key)} {payload}\nEX 300 (TTL 5 мин)
    end
end

GW --> Client : Request forwarded\n(tenant_id, permissions в headers)

note right of GW
  Ротация ключа: Redis TTL <= 5 мин.
  При revoke: PG revoked=true → Redis
  override TTL=0 (NFR-403).
end note

== Alt 2: Human (OAuth 2.0 / OIDC, Authorization Code + PKCE) ==

Browser -> IdP : GET /authorize\n?response_type=code&client_id=mlp\n&code_challenge=<S256>&redirect_uri=...

note right of IdP
  IdP: внешний провайдер
  (Keycloak / Okta / Azure AD).
  Описан в doc/2.04.
end note

IdP --> Browser : Login page
Browser -> IdP : POST credentials
IdP --> Browser : 302 redirect\n?code=<auth_code>

Browser -> GW : POST /auth/token\n{code, code_verifier, redirect_uri}
GW -> IdP : POST /token\n{code, code_verifier, client_secret}
IdP --> GW : {access_token (JWT RS256, TTL 15 мин),\nrefresh_token (TTL 7 дней)}

note right of GW
  JWT validation: подпись RS256,
  claims: exp, iss, aud.
  Публичные ключи IdP — JWKS cache TTL 1ч.
end note

GW -> GW : Verify JWT signature\n(JWKS cache, RS256)
GW --> Browser : 200 OK\n{access_token}\nSet-Cookie: refresh_token=...; HttpOnly; Secure

Browser -> GW : GET /v1/models\nAuthorization: Bearer <access_token>
GW -> GW : Verify JWT (exp, iss, aud, RS256)
GW --> Browser : 200 OK {models}

== Token Refresh (Access Token Expired) ==

Browser -> GW : GET /v1/models\nAuthorization: Bearer <expired_token>
GW --> Browser : 401 Unauthorized\nWWW-Authenticate: Bearer error="invalid_token"

Browser -> IdP : POST /token\n{grant_type=refresh_token,\nrefresh_token=<cookie>}
IdP --> Browser : {new access_token (TTL 15 мин)}
Browser -> GW : GET /v1/models\nAuthorization: Bearer <new_token>
GW --> Browser : 200 OK {models}

note over Client, IdP
  SSO (SAML 2.0 / корпоративный IdP) — extension point для MVP.
  Подключается без изменений в платформе: IdP меняется,
  протокол OIDC остаётся.
end note

@enduml
